<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"85f65623ddd4fa559f0fb7807add569d64fe3875","tid":1663434,"uid":160502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"死傻閪想玩分化<br />\n和勇永不割呀死柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bea034e11457678a5da9ac8659b512dc26efee9","tid":1663434,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5c4f2c6334885b2fdc3bcafb162e9f9fb72907","tid":1663434,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不推文回覆</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ef373f9c63df7cef52d74b8677cc98df0451e39","tid":1663434,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}